{"title":"Docker 操作","date":"2020-04-07T19:12:03.647Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年4月7日","L":"2020/04/07","MM-DD":"04-07"},"link":"2020/04/07/hello-world","updated":"2020-04-08T10:01:25.113Z","content":"<h3 id=\"docker-设置国内源：\">Docker 设置国内源：<a href=\"#docker-设置国内源：\" title=\"Docker 设置国内源：\"></a></h3><p><strong>/etc/docker/daemon.json</strong> 文件</p>\n<pre><code class=\"json\">{\n  <span class=\"attr\">\"registry-mirrors\"</span> : [\n    <span class=\"string\">\"https://mirrors.tencent.com\"</span>,\n    <span class=\"string\">\"http://hub-mirror.c.163.com\"</span>,\n    <span class=\"string\">\"https://docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn\"</span>,\n    <span class=\"string\">\"https://registry.docker-cn.com\"</span>\n  ]\n}</code></pre>\n<p><strong>国内加速地址有：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th align=\"right\">组织名称</th><th>地址</th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"right\">Docker中国官方</td><td><a href=\"https://registry.docker-cn.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://registry.docker-cn.com</a></td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">中国科技大学</td><td><a href=\"https://docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn\" target=\"_blank\">https://docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn</a></td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">Tencent开源库</td><td><a href=\"https://mirrors.tencent.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://mirrors.tencent.com</a></td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">网易</td><td><a href=\"http://hub-mirror.c.163.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://hub-mirror.c.163.com</a></td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br><h2 id=\"暂存\">暂存<a href=\"#暂存\" title=\"暂存\"></a></h2><ul><li><strong>在命令行退出容器，并使容器后台运行</strong>： <br><br><kbd>ctrl + p + q</kbd> <br><br>⚠️ 如果使用 <kbd>exit</kbd>指令会使容器停止。</li>\n</ul>","plink":"https://titor-z.github.io/2020/04/07/hello-world/","toc":[{"id":"docker-设置国内源：","title":"Docker 设置国内源：","index":"1"}]}